legacy.description: 1st Arab, African woman to lead UN Office at Vienna/ Office on Drugs & Crime @UNODC. Proud mother & grandmother, ⚽ fan who stands for fair play in life for all.
legacy.name: GhadaFathiWaly

legacy.full_text:
Happy to start my visit to China by meeting @UNODC partners & the Minister of Justice, to strengthen collaboration & explore avenues for South-South cooperation.

I also discussed with @cidcaofficial our work on access to legal aid, judicial reform & how to accelerate the #SDGs. https://t.co/qwyDCovi9J

Congratulations to @Ghadafathiwaly, DG of UNOV and ED of @UNODC on fruitful meetings with the Minister of Justice and high-level official of @cidcaofficial. We look forward to further deepening and expanding cooperation with UNODC.
